text: He amacya palanakartya! Amhi ase aikale ki eka pukaranara imanakade bolavita ahe ki lokanno! Apalya palanakartyavara imana rakha ani amhi imana rakhale. He amacya palanakartya! Ata tari amacya aparadhanna ksama kara ani amacya duskarmanna amacyapasuna dura kara ani neka sadacari lokansobata amhala mrtyu de
